COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to S.P. 240, L.D. 561
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment removes all the provisions of the bill regarding reimbursement based
33 on generally accepted payment practices. The amendment retains the provisions of the bill
44 that relate to payments based on enrollment rather than attendance. The amendment also
55 adds an appropriations and allocations section.
